creator: Learning Genie Inc
descriptionHtml:
Learning Genie is a reporting and portfolio app used in preschools and childcare centers. The customized experience allows you to be more present in your child’s early learning, establish a better relationship with teachers and share your feedback with ease.

• View your child's activities in real time updates and also through daily email reports
• Reinforce early learning at home with books, songs and other activities shared through the app
• Stay connected with school—receive announcements and reminders with ease

Note: Your child's school must be using the Learning Genie teacher's app in order for you to use the parent app. Talk to your school's director or contact us about using Learning Genie—it's easy to get started!
descriptionShort: Engage in your child’s early learning through photos, daily reports and more.

Learning Genie is a reporting and portfolio app used in preschools and childcare centers. The customized experience allows you to be more present in your child’s early learning, establish a better relationship with teachers and share your feedback with ease.

• View your child's activities in real time updates and also through daily email reports
• Reinforce early learning at home with books, songs and other activities shared through the app
• Stay connected with school—receive announcements and reminders with ease

Note: Your child's school must be using the Learning Genie teacher's app in order for you to use the parent app. Talk to your school's director or contact us about using Learning Genie—it's easy to get started!
descriptionShort: Engage in your child’s early learning through photos, daily reports and more.
